    "description": "This makes WindowPlotMPL axes and colorbars toggleable. I've created an example notebook where I cycle through the four plot layouts that are now possible:  \r\n\r\nhttp://nbviewer.ipython.org/url/hub.yt-project.org/notebooks/4d15a0ac0a4d4436b3166ba06ac14f67.ipynb\r\n\r\nTo get this working, I converted WindowPlotMPL into a state machine that calculates and caches the possible configurations of the plot the first time it is created in the new `_cache_layout` function.\r\n\r\nI've also included [e54809b](https://bitbucket.org/ngoldbaum/yt/commits/e54809b27344c746fe43f87170bb7b506bdcb7fd) which fixes @Guillochon's issue.",
